original_title: Inter-School Rugby: D. S. Senanayake College beat S. Thomas’ College, qualify for Super Round
original_body_lines: D. S. Senanayake continued their exceptional Under 19 Inter-School Rugby League season, qualifying for the Super Round from Group 1A along with defending champions Isipthana College, after beating S. Thomas' College 13-10 at Havelock Park.
They will be joined by the top two teams of Group 2A in the Super Round, with the four teams competing for the Under 19 schools league title.
